The paper proposes a boosting algorithm for label ranking tasks, which is a machine learning task. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with ranking and relevance, which are common themes in sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
